04:29.310 --> 04:32.352
- I'm sorry to be so early,
but there wasn't any traffic.

04:32.353 --> 04:34.795
Actually, I'm always early.
- That's all right. Come on in.

04:34.796 --> 04:36.757
Nadine Davies,
this is my daughter, Vicki.

04:36.758 --> 04:38.919
- Yeah, I introduced myself.
Um, if I could just talk to you

04:38.920 --> 04:40.521
