05:16.638 --> 05:19.920
- Well, I have nothing against
a good cup of coffee.

05:19.921 --> 05:21.922
-How old's your daughter?

05:21.923 --> 05:25.766
- She's Charlie's daughter
from his first marriage.

05:25.767 --> 05:27.529
Afraid I'm the other woman.

05:30.812 --> 05:32.452
- Are you okay?
- Yeah, I'm good.

05:32.453 --> 05:34.254
It's... It's healing fine.
No damage.

05:34.255 --> 05:35.936
- Well, not that.
You just seem...

05:35.937 --> 05:37.377
-I'm good. Let's go, let's go.

05:37.378 --> 05:39.259
- Okay, well, this is
what I got so far.

05:39.260 --> 05:41.381
You want more,
I can "drone" her backyard.

05:41.382 --> 05:43.023
- Drone?
- Yeah, it's no big thing.

05:43.024 --> 05:45.465
Uh, bank accounts...
Joint with her husband.

05:45.466 --> 05:48.669
Investment portfolio...
Impressive, well-managed.

05:48.670 --> 05:50.671
And then there's this
one Citibank account.

05:50.672 --> 05:52.232
-Shh, shh, shh.

05:52.233 --> 05:54.795
Um, she opened it 33 years ago,

05:54.796 --> 05:58.478
put $50,000 a year in
for the next 12 years.

05:58.479 --> 06:00.080
Since then,
it remained untouched,

06:00.081 --> 06:07.407
accruing away... $1,773, 480.18
as of last quarter.

06:07.408 --> 06:10.691
You smelled it.

06:10.692 --> 06:14.414
She had a kid when she was 17.

06:14.415 --> 06:16.577
Put him up for adoption.

06:16.578 --> 06:18.138
And her search history?

06:18.139 --> 06:20.140
Been lookin' at
a lot of middle schools.

06:20.141 --> 06:22.503
- For a kid who's 30?
- Bingo.

06:22.504 --> 06:24.384
See, here she
is sitting quietly,

06:24.385 --> 06:27.628
listening to people talk
in a survivor-guilt chat room.

06:27.629 --> 06:31.431
So, I come in, talk about a kid
I had that I put up for adoption

06:31.432 --> 06:34.635
and found out he died
and I was devastated.

06:34.636 --> 06:37.118
And there she is.

06:41.202 --> 06:44.605
- He died when he was 13?
- 12.

06:44.606 --> 06:48.569
You want to see a picture?

06:48.570 --> 06:50.611
-You get a name?

06:50.612 --> 06:52.172
-I got two.

06:52.173 --> 06:53.814
- You know why Charlie
wanted to see me?

06:53.815 --> 06:56.537
- Oh, when it comes to
the business, it is all him.

06:56.538 --> 06:58.058
I mean, like I said
when we first met,

06:58.059 --> 06:59.339
I'm really just a housewife.

06:59.340 --> 07:00.541
-Mm.

07:00.542 --> 07:02.022
- Linda giving you
Dad's coffee rap?

07:02.023 --> 07:03.744
- Water just below boiling,
coffee weighed.

07:03.745 --> 07:05.265
- Hey.
- I like a ritual.

07:05.266 --> 07:06.787
-And I like good coffee.

07:06.788 --> 07:08.268
- Any left?
- Yeah, I'll make you a cup.

07:08.269 --> 07:09.790
- Do you want to come
into the office?

07:09.791 --> 07:11.311
You can bring your coffee
if you like.

07:11.312 --> 07:12.953
- Would it be insulting
to ask for sugar?

07:12.954 --> 07:14.795
- Ooh.
- A little bit.

07:14.796 --> 07:16.797
But I'm handling it.

07:16.798 --> 07:19.439
All I ask is
that you try it first,

07:19.440 --> 07:23.483
and then, if you still want
to sweeten it up...

07:23.484 --> 07:26.047
I don't want to be disturbed
under any circumstances.

07:29.811 --> 07:31.732
I hope you weren't expecting
a crystal ball

07:31.733 --> 07:33.453
or anything like that.

07:33.454 --> 07:35.255
- Tell you the truth, I don't
know what I was expecting.

07:35.256 --> 07:37.658
I do use tarot cards
from time to time,

07:37.659 --> 07:40.581
not because I honestly believe
that the order

07:40.582 --> 07:42.783
in which you turn over the cards
can reveal anything

07:42.784 --> 07:45.305
about your future
or your spiritual life,

07:45.306 --> 07:46.827
because I do believe

07:46.828 --> 07:49.149
that they can
be powerful symbols

07:49.150 --> 07:52.793
in unlocking certain
characteristics

07:52.794 --> 07:54.795
in both participants
in a reading.

07:54.796 --> 07:57.998
- Is what this is going to be,
a reading? I mean, I thought...

07:57.999 --> 07:59.840
Well, you called and said
it was important,

07:59.841 --> 08:03.844
and, well, I imagined it was
about the Gypsies.

08:03.845 --> 08:07.007
- That's for you.
It's $5,000.

08:07.008 --> 08:08.328
-I don't understand.

08:08.329 --> 08:10.170
-Well, I told you I knew a cop.

08:10.171 --> 08:13.373
The Roma... They tend to have
big, extended families.

08:13.374 --> 08:14.895
He dug something up...

08:14.896 --> 08:17.858
Well, a few things about
your psychic's cousins

08:17.859 --> 08:19.540
and what they were involved in.

08:19.541 --> 08:21.141
Guys drive around supermarkets

08:21.142 --> 08:23.504
telling people they can repair
the dents in their cars.

08:23.505 --> 08:25.145
Sometimes
they steal their money,

08:25.146 --> 08:26.947
and sometimes
they steal their cars.

08:26.948 --> 08:28.869
Anyway, we convinced her
to take $15,000

08:28.870 --> 08:30.831
and go back to Ohio
with her cousins

08:30.832 --> 08:32.753
and never come back.

08:32.754 --> 08:34.193
You're never gonna
be bothered again.

08:34.195 --> 08:36.236
-I-I can't thank you enough.

08:36.236 --> 08:37.999
-It was my pleasure, believe me.

08:41.442 --> 08:44.765
- You know, I'm sorry that
someone as obviously open

08:44.766 --> 08:47.728
and curious as you are had
the experience you had.

08:47.729 --> 08:49.770
- Sorry.
Oop.

08:49.771 --> 08:52.533
I'm actually, as a rule,
not all that gullible.

08:52.534 --> 08:54.575
- But you don't seem to
automatically expect

08:54.576 --> 08:56.216
the worst in others.

08:56.217 --> 08:58.458
- Uh, that sounds like
a line from a reading.

08:58.459 --> 09:01.061
-That is a Barnum statement.

09:01.062 --> 09:03.944
It's a broad statement
that can be true of anybody.

09:03.945 --> 09:05.225
-Thanks.

09:05.226 --> 09:06.987
- It's a popular tool
in mentalism,

09:06.988 --> 09:08.589
that sort of magic.

09:08.590 --> 09:10.831
- Linda said that you were
a magician.

09:10.832 --> 09:14.595
How did you, um, switch teams?

09:14.596 --> 09:17.157
- Oh, that's a bit of a story.
- I'm curious.

09:17.158 --> 09:20.160
- My dad died when I was five.
- I'm so sorry.

09:20.161 --> 09:22.843
-For me, it was what it was.

09:22.844 --> 09:26.086
But it broke my mother's heart.

09:26.087 --> 09:31.091
She visited a-a woman
who claimed to be a psychic.

09:31.092 --> 09:34.214
She told her my father
was nearby,

09:34.215 --> 09:36.857
trying to warn her
that she was in danger,

09:36.858 --> 09:38.418
and she was in danger,
all right.

09:38.419 --> 09:40.781
The psychic took her
for everything...

09:40.782 --> 09:44.024
All her savings,
the deed to our trailer.

09:44.025 --> 09:46.507
I mean, we lived on the street
for almost a year.

09:46.508 --> 09:47.788
-That's terrible.

09:47.789 --> 09:49.389
-Oh, it got worse.

09:49.390 --> 09:52.232
She dove headfirst into a
vodka bottle and never came out.

09:52.233 --> 09:56.436
I was 14, and my sister
was 10 when she died.

09:56.437 --> 09:58.158
- So, Dad said to mention,
in case it comes up,

09:58.159 --> 09:59.520
he's going with the, uh...

09:59.521 --> 10:01.522
The "trailer park/bad
psychic" story,

10:01.523 --> 10:03.684
not the one where
his mom has lymphoma.

10:03.685 --> 10:04.965
-Yeah, I-I figured.

10:04.966 --> 10:06.647
Trailer park's
a little more real.

10:06.648 --> 10:09.489
- You ever notice how,
in both stories, Grandpa dies?

10:09.490 --> 10:11.972
- I think that's called
wish fulfillment.

10:11.973 --> 10:13.814
Did you want more?
I can make more.

10:13.815 --> 10:15.536
-No, I got to go to work.

10:15.537 --> 10:18.179
Can't start doggin' it until
they realize I'm invaluable.

10:23.384 --> 10:25.265
Good luck with that.

10:25.266 --> 10:29.309
- Linda told me that you
actually were, well, psychic.

10:29.310 --> 10:34.675
- Sometimes, I have intuitions
that are helpful.

10:34.676 --> 10:37.157
Sometimes, the cards
can be helpful.

10:37.158 --> 10:38.679
But I don't know.

10:38.680 --> 10:41.642
I mean, maybe it's just
a question of focus.

10:41.643 --> 10:45.365
- You must be the world's
most self-deprecating psychic.

10:45.366 --> 10:48.889
- Well, I'm just glad
that you're safe, Nadine,

10:48.890 --> 10:52.173
and that we were able to get you
some of your money back.

10:54.696 --> 10:57.097
- Uh, the other day,
when you were at my house,

10:57.098 --> 10:59.900
you stopped and said
that you had, um...

10:59.901 --> 11:02.382
a feeling.
Was that this intuition?

11:02.383 --> 11:05.866
- Just for a moment,
I-I felt a presence.

11:05.867 --> 11:08.468
It could've been that,
or maybe it's just the situation

11:08.469 --> 11:09.790
you're in with the Gypsies.

11:09.791 --> 11:12.472
-There's that self-deprecation.

11:12.473 --> 11:14.074
Could you...

11:14.075 --> 11:16.957
Do you think
that you could, um...

11:16.958 --> 11:18.478
find it again?
- Find it?

11:18.479 --> 11:20.040
-The presence you felt.

11:20.041 --> 11:23.483
I mean, you said
sometimes the cards...

11:23.484 --> 11:27.367
-Oh.

11:27.368 --> 11:29.370
You want me
to give you a reading.

11:35.416 --> 11:37.497
-Well, no surprise here.

11:37.498 --> 11:40.060
This card represents
strife, competition,

11:40.061 --> 11:42.743
feeling beat up, under attack...

11:42.744 --> 11:45.265
You know, like when someone
pulls down a tree

11:45.266 --> 11:47.387
and leaves a rooster
with a crown on its head

11:47.388 --> 11:49.029
in your bedroom to scare you.

11:49.030 --> 11:51.111
-Mm.

11:51.112 --> 11:52.633
-The three of cups.

11:52.634 --> 11:54.835
Abundant life, long term,

11:54.836 --> 11:58.559
surrounded by good food
and wine, good friends.

11:58.560 --> 12:00.120
Sometimes, as I said,

12:00.121 --> 12:02.643
the tarot just tells us
what we already know.

12:02.644 --> 12:04.605
- I'm actually more
of a beer person.

12:04.606 --> 12:06.446
-To be honest, so am I.

12:06.447 --> 12:08.847
When these things were made,
they were probably talking mead.

12:09.811 --> 12:11.211
-Mm.

12:11.212 --> 12:13.574
- What?
- This, uh...

12:13.575 --> 12:15.576
This is the cheaters card.

12:15.577 --> 12:20.541
Someone is taking something,
being sneaky, unfaithful,

12:20.542 --> 12:23.784
acting without integrity.

12:23.785 --> 12:26.266
Your husband's business trips...

12:26.267 --> 12:28.028
-Didn't take a psychic.

12:28.029 --> 12:30.230
- Well, as I said,
sometimes the cards

12:30.231 --> 12:32.873
just tell you
what you already know.

12:37.198 --> 12:40.280
- Surprise.
- What are you doing here?

12:40.281 --> 12:43.804
- I got you something.
Charlie's not home?

12:43.805 --> 12:46.648
- Charlie's with a client.
He's not to be disturbed.

12:58.820 --> 13:02.102
- One time, in high school,
I went home with this guy.

13:02.103 --> 13:04.625
I mean, he took me to his place.
It was his parents' place.

13:04.626 --> 13:06.426
They were out of town.

13:06.427 --> 13:08.348
So, we're doing it
in his parents' bedroom.

13:08.349 --> 13:10.871
I mean, we're trying.
He's a kid.

13:10.872 --> 13:12.633
You know how boys get.

13:12.634 --> 13:16.837
So I whisper in his ear,
"This is your parents' bed.

13:16.838 --> 13:20.480
We're doing it
in your parents' bed."

13:20.481 --> 13:24.685
He gets rock hard,
and we fuck for hours.

13:24.686 --> 13:26.486
Sometimes, if there was a lull,

13:26.487 --> 13:29.089
I just had to remind him
where we were.

13:29.090 --> 13:32.372
- Good to know.
- Take me to your room.

13:32.373 --> 13:34.254
You said he's with a client.

13:34.255 --> 13:36.737
- You may find this hard
to believe...

13:36.738 --> 13:40.020
