if I were you.

14:21.462 --> 14:24.666
Like I said, too much...
Not a good thing.

14:28.950 --> 14:32.152
- You said you wanted
to go to my room?

14:32.153 --> 14:34.675
- Yeah.
You changing your mind?

14:34.676 --> 14:36.316
-Well, I was just wondering.

14:36.317 --> 14:40.160
You've got this stuff,
you know how well it works.

14:40.161 --> 14:41.802
