14:41.803 --> 14:44.364
We'd be in there right now,
under my sheets.

14:44.365 --> 14:47.447
-The thought crossed my mind.

14:47.448 --> 14:51.011
Seriously, it did.

14:52.574 --> 14:56.537
It's gonna sound like
a Hallmark card, but...

